metadata.description:
This Mercury uwu Quest stamp was created by [FahFahs](https://twitter.com/fahfahsnft) as a bid reward for their [Systema Solaris Foundation Piece](https://foundation.app/@uwucrew/systemasolaris/1).

Systema Solaris quest stamps were dropped to snapshotted holders on 6/4/2022 and bidders of the [Systema Solaris Foundation Collection](https://mirror.xyz/uwucrew.eth/_R5xzweyufF3uUaFeTUr_vgmIJ--XPvaKNWA2ajUmXg)!

They can be used in various uwu Quest recipes to redeem special prizes: [Read about uwu Quest here](https://mirror.xyz/uwucrew.eth/_4n9TUszNT23Eiby-vGwcaZDTjGCBWmwooMG9gLCzi0)
metadata.name: Mercury by FahFahs
